# DS-0002: Lambda base images (public.ecr.aws/lambda/python:*) require root.
# The AWS Lambda Runtime bootstrap (/var/runtime/bootstrap) must run as UID 0.
# Adding USER non-root breaks the invocation path. Checkov CKV_DOCKER_3 is also
# suppressed in each Dockerfile for the same reason. Re-evaluate if any Lambda
# image migrates to python:3.12-slim + awslambdaric (as rest-api/Dockerfile does).
DS-0002

